  "title": "Locum Aesthetic Doctor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Lazz Aesthetic is a professional Aesthetic Medical Clinic. Our client is from mid to high end. Our commitment is to deliver scientifically proven evidence-based aesthetic and age management treatments with genuine care. Our employees are passionately committed to fundamentally change the future of medical aesthetic and age management care.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform medical-grade aesthetic treatments including injectables (Botox, skin boosters, fillers), Pico Laser, Helio laser treatments, chemical peels, and thread lifts to achieve optimal patient outcomes</li><li>Develop and recommend personalized patient treatment plans based on thorough assessment of patient concerns and clinical indications</li><li>Conduct detailed patient consultations to educate and advise on treatment options, expected results, and care protocols</li><li>Monitor and review patient progress regularly to adjust treatment plans and ensure high standards of care and safety</li><li>Manage patient enquiries effectively, providing clear information about treatment courses and addressing concerns to enhance patient satisfaction</li><li>Train and mentor clinical staff on aesthetic procedures and patient care standards to maintain consistent service quality</li><li>Foster a collaborative and respectful workplace environment that supports performance excellence and patient-centered care</li><li>Promote a friendly, warm, and exceptional patient experience throughout all clinical interactions</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Medical degree such as MBBS, MBChB, MBBCh, MD, or equivalent</li><li>Registration as a medical doctor with the Singapore Medical Council</li><li>Attainment of all relevant Certificate of Competence (COCs) for aesthetic procedures</li></ul>",
